UBUNTU:
After flashing SD card create file called "ssh" to enable ssh login during first raspberry boot.
Ubuntu user is created by default during flashing SD-card. Initial credential after flashing SD card ubuntu:ubuntu.
During first login we are forced to change password for ubuntu user. This password should be provided during playbook execution. 

ansible-playbook playbooks/initial_configuration.yml -i inventory --ask-pass --ask-vault-pass